{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/hofstadter-q-sequence","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"rosetta-code-challenges","demoType":null,"title":"Niz Hofstadtera Q","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Niz Hofstadtera Q je definisan kao:</p>\n<p>$Q(1)=Q(2)=1, \\\\ Q(n)=Q\\big(n-Q(n-1)\\big)+Q\\big(n-Q(n-2)), \\quad n>2.$</p>\n<p>Definisano je kao Fibonacci niz, ali umesto da je sledeći broj u Fibonacci nizu zbir dva prethodna broja, u Q nizu, dva prethodna broja ukazuju na koliko daleko nazad u Q niz treba pronaći dva broja za sabiranje kako bi se dobio sledeći broj niza.</p>\n</section>","id":"59637c4d89f6786115efd814","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Implementiraj Hofstadter Q sekvencijsku jednačinu kao funkciju. Funkcija treba da primi broj, <code>n</code>, i vrati ceo broj.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Rosetta","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"rosetta-code","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302287,"hooks":{"beforeAll":null,"beforeEach":"const testCase = [1000, 1500, 2000, 2500];\nconst res = [502, 755, 1005, 1261];","afterEach":null,"afterAll":null},"fields":{"slug":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/hofstadter-q-sequence"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function hofstadterQ(n) {\n\n  return n;\n}","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>hofstadterQ</code> Trebalo bi da bude funkcija.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof hofstadterQ === 'function');"},{"text":"<p><code>hofstadterQ()</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>integer</code></p>","testString":"assert(Number.isInteger(hofstadterQ(1000)));"},{"text":"<p><code>hofstadterQ(1000)</code> treba da vrati <code>502</code></p>","testString":"assert.equal(hofstadterQ(testCase[0]), res[0]);"},{"text":"<p><code>hofstadterQ(1500)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>755</code></p>","testString":"assert.equal(hofstadterQ(testCase[1]), res[1]);"},{"text":"<p><code>hofstadterQ(2000)</code> treba vratiti <code>1005</code></p>","testString":"assert.equal(hofstadterQ(testCase[2]), res[2]);"},{"text":"<p><code>hofstadterQ(2500)</code> treba da vrati <code>1261</code></p>","testString":"assert.equal(hofstadterQ(testCase[3]), res[3]);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/rosetta-code/#rosetta-code-challenges","dashedName":"hofstadter-q-sequence","certification":"rosetta-code","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"rosetta-code","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"rosetta-code-challenges","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/i-before-e-except-after-c","prevChallengePath":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/hofstadter-figure-figure-sequences","id":"59637c4d89f6786115efd814","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function ZigZagMatrix(n) {\n  const mtx = [];\n  for (let i = 0; i < n; i++) {\n    mtx[i] = [];\n  }\n\n  let i = 1;\n  let j = 1;\n  for (let e = 0; e < n * n; e++) {\n    mtx[i - 1][j - 1] = e;\n    if ((i + j) % 2 === 0) {\n      // Even stripes\n      if (j < n) j++;\n      else i += 2;\n      if (i > 1) i--;\n    } else {\n      // Odd stripes\n      if (i < n) i++;\n      else j += 2;\n      if (j > 1) j--;\n    }\n  }\n  return mtx;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/hofstadter-q-sequence"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}